    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31 | 30 | 29 | 28:24 | 23:22 | 21 | 20 | 19:16 | 15 | 14 | 13:12 | 11 | 10 | 9:5 | 4:0 |
    /// | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
    /// |  | Q | U |  | size | L | M | Rm | opcode<3> | opcode<2> | opcode<1:0> | H |  | Rn | Rd |
