    /// # BTI
    ///
    /// Branch Target Identification
    ///
    /// - `BTI  {<targets>}` — System
    ///
    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31:22 | 21 | 20:19 | 18:16 | 15:12 | 11:8 | 7:5 | 4:0 |
