    /// - `<T>` — For the vector single-precision and double-precision variant: is an arrangement specifier, 0 → 0, 0 → 1, 1 → 0, 1 → 1
    /// - `<Vn>` — Is the name of the first SIMD&FP source register, encoded in the "Rn" field.
