    /// - `FCADD  <Vd>.<T>, <Vn>.<T>, <Vm>.<T>, #<rotate>` — Vector
    ///
    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31 | 30 | 29 | 28:24 | 23:22 | 21 | 20:16 | 15 | 14:13 | 12 | 11 | 10 | 9:5 | 4:0 |
    /// | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
    /// |  | Q | U |  | size |  | Rm |  |  | rot |  |  | Rn | Rd |
