    /// - `<Tb>` — Is an arrangement specifier, 0 → 2H, 1 → 4H
    /// - `<Vm>` — Is the name of the second SIMD&FP source register, encoded in the "Rm" field.
    /// - `<index>` — Is the element index, encoded in the "H:L:M" fields.
