    /// - `GMI  <Xd>, <Xn|SP>, <Xm>` — Integer
    ///
    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31 | 30 | 29 | 28:21 | 20:16 | 15 | 14 | 13 | 12 | 11 | 10 | 9:5 | 4:0 |
    /// | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
    /// | sf |  | S |  | Xm | opcode<5> | opcode<4> | opcode<3> | opcode<2> | opcode<1> | opcode<0> | Xn | Xd |
