    /// - `<amount>` — For the 16-bit shifted immediate variant: is the shift amount 0 → 0, 1 → 8 defaulting to 0 if LSL is omitted.
    /// - `<amount>` — For the 32-bit shifted immediate variant: is the shift amount 00 → 0, 01 → 8, 10 → 16, 11 → 24 defaulting to 0 if LSL is omitted.
