    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31:24 | 23 | 22 | 21 | 20 | 19 | 18 | 17 | 16 | 15 | 14 | 13 | 12 | 11 | 10 | 9:5 | 4:0 |
    /// | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
    /// |  | opc<1> | opc<0> |  | imm9<8> | imm9<7> | imm9<6> | imm9<5> | imm9<4> | imm9<3> | imm9<2> | imm9<1> | imm9<0> | op2<1> | op2<0> | Xn | Xt |
