    /// # SUB (extended register)
    ///
    /// Subtract (extended register)
    ///
    /// - `SUB  <Wd|WSP>, <Wn|WSP>, <Wm>{, <extend> {#<amount>}}` — 32-bit
    /// - `SUB  <Xd|SP>, <Xn|SP>, <R><m>{, <extend> {#<amount>}}` — 64-bit
