    /// # SUQADD
    ///
    /// Signed saturating Accumulate of Unsigned value
    ///
    /// - `SUQADD  <V><d>, <V><n>` — Scalar
    /// - `SUQADD  <Vd>.<T>, <Vn>.<T>` — Vector
