    /// - `TBX  <Vd>.<Ta>, { <Vn>.16B, <Vn+1>.16B, <Vn+2>.16B, <Vn+3>.16B }, <Vm>.<Ta>` — Four register table
    /// - `TBX  <Vd>.<Ta>, { <Vn>.16B }, <Vm>.<Ta>` — Single register table
