    /// # TRN1
    ///
    /// Transpose vectors (primary)
    ///
    /// - `TRN1  <Vd>.<T>, <Vn>.<T>, <Vm>.<T>` — Advanced SIMD
    ///
    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31 | 30 | 29:24 | 23:22 | 21 | 20:16 | 15 | 14 | 13:12 | 11:10 | 9:5 | 4:0 |
    /// | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
