    /// # UADDL, UADDL2
    ///
    /// Unsigned Add Long (vector)
    ///
    /// - `UADDL{2}  <Vd>.<Ta>, <Vn>.<Tb>, <Vm>.<Tb>` — Three registers, not all the same type
    ///
    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31 | 30 | 29 | 28:24 | 23:22 | 21 | 20:16 | 15:14 | 13 | 12 | 11:10 | 9:5 | 4:0 |
