    /// # UDF
    ///
    /// Permanently Undefined
    ///
    /// - `UDF  #<imm>` — Integer
    ///
    /// ## Encoding
    ///
    /// | 31:16 | 15:0 |
    /// | --- | --- |
    /// |  | imm16 |
